# 🛡️ RoadGuard — Complete Project Documentation
## Advanced Pothole Detection & Road Safety System

> A Raspberry Pi–powered smart vehicle system that detects potholes using AI (YOLOv8), monitors road conditions with IMU sensors, and displays everything in real-time on a beautiful web dashboard.

---

