1. [Section 1 — File & Folder Structure](#section-1--file--folder-structure)
2. [Section 2 — Step-by-Step Setup Guide (From Zero)](#section-2--step-by-step-setup-guide-from-zero)
3. [Section 3 — How Everything Works](#section-3--how-everything-works)

